 eNCA senior reporter Siphamandla Goge is at that Lekgotla monitoring these developments. EKURHULENI - The ANC probably has its most difficult election campaign ahead of it, that's the view of party president Cyril Ramaphosa. He says the ANC needs to be in campaign mode as the 2024 elections will have what he calls 'profound implications'. He was delivering the opening remarks at the NEC Lekgotla meeting in Ekurhuleni.